-- Netherlands, Denmark Tied 0-0 at Halftime in World Cup Soccer Group E
-- Alex Duff
-- 2010-06-14T12:17:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-14/netherlands-denmark-tied-0-0-at-halftime-in-world-cup-soccer-group-e.html

          
          
             The Netherlands and Denmark were
tied 0-0 at halftime in their opening World Cup soccer game at
Soccer City stadium in Johannesburg.  
 The Dutch are fifth-favorite to win the tournament at 9-1
with Vienna-based Bwin.com behind Spain, Brazil, Argentina and
Germany. A successful $1 bet would yield a $9 profit.  
          
          


  


        